\">HMRC</abbr>-NMW)</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p>The Director will set a strategy and create an intelligence hub enabling data sharing between the director, enforcement bodies and other bodies with intelligence.</p>\n\n<p><a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/government/organisations/employment-agency-standards-inspectorate\">Employment Agency Standards Inspectorate</a>, <a rel=\"external\" href=\"http://www.gla.gov.uk/who-we-are/our-aims-and-objectives/the-gangmasters-and-labour-abuse-authority/\">Gangmasters &amp; Labour Abuse Authority</a> and <a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/government/organisations/hm-revenue-customs\">HM Revenue &amp; Customs</a></p>\n\n<h2 id=\"reports\">Reports</h2>\n\n<ul>\n  <li><a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/government/publications/labour-market-enforcement-annual-report-2018-to-2019\">Labour Market Enforcement: annual report 2018 to 2019</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/government/consultations/labour-market-enforcement-strategy-2020-to-2021-call-for-evidence\">Labour Market Enforcement Strategy 2020 to 2021: call for evidence</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/government/publications/labour-market-enforcement-strategy-2019-to-2020\">Labour Market Enforcement Strategy 2019 to 2020</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/government/consultations/labour-market-enforcement-strategy-2019-to-2020-call-for-evidence\">Labour Market Enforcement Strategy 2019 to 2020: call for evidence</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/government/publications/labour-market-enforcement-strategy-2018-to-2019\">Labour Market Enforcement Strategy 2018 to 2019</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/government/publications/labour-market-enforcement-strategy-introductory-report\">Labour Market Enforcement Strategy: introductory report</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/government/publications/labour-market-enforcement-annual-report-2017-to-2018\">Labour Market Enforcement: annual report 2017 to 2018</a></li>\n</ul>\n\n","role_payment_type":nu